stack: React, Remotion, TypeScript

@EXPORTS
index.ts: registerRoot(RemotionRoot) — app entry point
Root.tsx: RemotionRoot — registers all 18 compositions

@VARS_CONSTANTS
FPS: number = 30 — frame rate
W: number = 1920 — width
H: number = 1080 — height

@FUNCTIONS
RemotionRoot() → React.FC
  purpose: register all compositions + load fonts
  side-effects: font loading (Montserrat, IBM Plex Mono, Phosphor 6 weights)

@PROCESSES
boot: index.ts → registerRoot → Root.tsx → font loading → 18 compositions

@INTERFACES
Compositions: BrandShowcase | FrameShowcase | TypographyShowcase | IconShowcase | ChapterIntro | IntroAnimation | BarChartDemo | NeuralNetDemo | RAGDemo | TerminalDemo | TopTenDemo | CardsShowcase | CTAShowcase | BackgroundsShowcase | EducationalShowcase | ExplainerVideo | ShortVideo | EP01

@DEPENDENCIES
internal: styles/tokens | components/* | compositions/* | hooks/*
external: remotion | @remotion/google-fonts

@STANDARDS
- Montserrat weights 500-800, subsets latin + latin-ext
- IBM Plex Mono weights 400-500, subsets latin + latin-ext
- ShortVideo uses 1080x1920 (9:16), all others 1920x1080
- EP01 is 38160 frames (~21 min) — production episode "10 Mýtů o AI"
